debilitating side effects.

7
00:00:22,322 --> 00:00:24,257
That sounds perfect.

8
00:00:24,324 --> 00:00:25,451
It's exactly what he wanted.

9
00:00:25,526 --> 00:00:27,825
All right. Dr. Sharpe
gets it done.

10
00:00:27,895 --> 00:00:30,296
Which is the difference
between me and this trial.

11
00:00:30,397 --> 00:00:32,229
Because precision
therapy might not work.

12
00:00:32,299 --> 00:00:34,666
Your objection is noted. Again.

13
00:00:34,735 --> 00:00:37,432
Yes, radiation
chemotherapy is challenging,

14
00:00:37,504 --> 00:00:38,938
but it's... It's brutal.

15
00:00:39,006 --> 00:00:41,498
It's hitting yourself with a
brick over and over again

16
00:00:41,575 --> 00:00:43,908
and hoping the cancer
dies first. That's the point.

17
00:00:43,977 --> 00:00:45,707
The cancer dies.

18
00:00:46,213 --> 00:00:48,409
Radiation and chemotherapy work.

19
00:00:48,549 --> 00:00:51,644
