gambling your life on a lottery ticket.

20
00:00:51,718 --> 00:00:54,119
People said the same thing
about bone marrow transplants.

21
00:00:54,187 --> 00:00:55,985
They also say it
about lottery tickets.

22
00:00:56,056 --> 00:00:57,183
Enough.

23
00:01:00,994 --> 00:01:02,826
Is this what you really want?

24
00:01:10,270 --> 00:01:11,499
She's right.

25
00:01:11,572 --> 00:01:14,041
Chemo and radiation, they work.

26
00:01:14,174 --> 00:01:15,369
They do the job.

27
00:01:15,842 --> 00:01:19,040
But they'll break me.

28
00:01:20,047 --> 00:01:23,540
No matter how strong I
am. I'll lose my hearing.

29
00:01:24,084 --> 00:01:25,518
My sight.

30
00:01:27,220 --> 00:01:29,052
I'll lose my mind.

31
00:01:29,690 --> 00:01:31,625
They don't always come back.

32
00:01:32,793 --> 00:01:34,887
And I have so many things

33
