you should definitely be groveling.

40
00:02:11,565 --> 00:02:13,727
Evie and I were up
all night. You stallion.

41
00:02:14,001 --> 00:02:16,095
Fighting. Look, I'm not
trying to be a jerk here,

42
00:02:16,169 --> 00:02:17,529
but telling Evie
that we used to...

43
