I know. It wasn't cool.

44
00:02:19,139 --> 00:02:20,835
I said I know.

45
00:02:20,907 --> 00:02:23,342
What you should be
saying is, "I am sorry."

46
00:02:24,244 --> 00:02:26,179
I am. I'm sorry.

47
00:02:26,446 --> 00:02:28,005
