It's French vanilla.

54
00:02:47,534 --> 00:02:48,797
Like hell it is.

55
00:02:48,935 --> 00:02:50,631
Eh, maybe hazelnut?

56
00:02:50,771 --> 00:02:52,535
You're mothering
me or babying me.

57
00:02:52,606 --> 00:02:54,199
Whichever one it is, stop it.

58
00:02:54,374 --> 00:02:56,275
Are you okay?
You're doing it again.

59
00:02:56,343 --> 00:02:58,574
What do we got? This
is LaDavius Powell,

60
00:02:58,645 --> 00:03:02,446
45-year-old man with new
onset right-side abdominal pain.

61
00:03:02,516 --> 00:03:05,782
No meds, no past medical
history, allergic to Cephalkem.

62
00:03:05,852 --> 00:03:07,320
Cephalkem? Fancy penicillin.

63
00:03:07,387 --> 00:03:09,379
Bay 23, step lively. Cephalkem.

64
