Right over there.

251
00:11:29,055 --> 00:11:30,853
And the amazing thing is,

252
00:11:31,024 --> 00:11:32,617
she gets another chance.

253
00:11:34,460 --> 00:11:37,953
Thirty years ago, the doctors
here let Luna's heart stop.

254
00:11:40,366 --> 00:11:41,834
Not this time.

255
00:11:51,044 --> 00:11:53,013
Hey. Uh, Evie.

256
00:11:53,646 --> 00:11:55,308
