I always hide the
bodies when I'm done.

260
00:12:06,859 --> 00:12:09,522
I... That was not
even a little bit funny.

261
00:12:10,363 --> 00:12:13,162
Okay, uh, listen.

262
00:12:13,533 --> 00:12:16,833
The other day when I mentioned
that Reynolds and I, we...

263
00:12:17,670 --> 00:12:19,104
We kind of had this, uh,

