00:12:28,448 --> 00:12:29,677
sisters.

269
00:12:29,749 --> 00:12:31,377
Or whatever.

270
00:12:31,584 --> 00:12:34,179
I think you and Reynolds
are perfect for each other.

271
00:12:34,254 --> 00:12:36,655
I mean, that's why I
introduced the two of you, so...

272
00:12:36,723 --> 00:12:38,885
Let me bail you out here.
Oh, great, please hurry.

273
00:12:38,958 --> 00:12:41,325
I know Floyd had
a life before me.

274
00:12:41,394 --> 00:12:42,692
I'm glad he did.

275
00:12:42,762 --> 00:12:44,697
I just need to know
if you two are over.

276
00:12:45,098 --> 00:12:46,964
Oh! Oh, we're over.

277
00:12:47,033 --> 00:12:48,968
We are the very
definition of over.

278
00:12:49,736 --> 00:12:51,102
I like Floyd.

279
00:12:51,271 --> 00:12:53,570
But I've made bad bets before.

280
00:12:54,407 --> 00:12:58,435
So if you really are a card-carrying
member of the sisterhood of sisters,

281
00:12:59,412 --> 00:13:01,381
you won't let me do it again.

282
00:13:02,248 --> 00:13:04,717
Because I do not have time.

283
00:13:06,219 --> 00:13:08,882
So are you and Floyd done?

284
00:13:09,989 --> 00:13:11,480
Evie.

285
00:13:11,791 --> 00:13:14,659
It is not something that you
have to worry about. Okay?

286
00:13:15,795 --> 00:13:16,990
Then I won't.

287
00:13:18,331 --> 00:13:19,424
Okay.

288
00:13:36,916 --> 00:13:38,680
That looks fun.

289
00:13:38,751 --> 00:13:43,189
This infusion replaces the clotting
factor that your body is destroying.

290
00:13:43,256 --> 00:13:45,691
So you can just replace
it? It's that simple?

291
00:13:45,758 --> 00:13:48,250
Unfortunately, it's
not simple at all.

292
00:13:48,328 --> 00:13:49,762
Uh, but it's very doable.

293
00:13:49,829 --> 00:13:52,993
It's been done
successfully many times.

294
00:13:53,299 --> 00:13:54,699
We need to infuse the factor

295
00:13:54,767 --> 00:13:56,512
at the exact same rate that
your body is destroying it,

296
00:13:56,536 --> 00:13:58,801
which is an incredibly
difficult rate to find.

297
00:13:58,871 --> 00:14:00,772
But again, doable.

298
00:14:01,307 --> 00:14:03,538
Too much factor and
your blood will clot.

299
00:14:04,177 --> 00:14:05,406
