00:21:08,067 --> 00:21:09,535
What the heck. Yeah.

446
00:21:09,602 --> 00:21:11,537
Just no video, okay?

447
00:21:11,604 --> 00:21:15,234
All right, so. Do you see the
dark spots here on the ends?

