you that I want you to have the surgery.

470
00:22:25,711 --> 00:22:27,304
I said so to your parents.

471
00:22:27,513 --> 00:22:30,142
Screw this, and screw you.

472
00:22:30,316 --> 00:22:31,477
Okay.

473
00:22:32,718 --> 00:22:34,050
Okay, thanks.

474
00:22:34,119 --> 00:22:35,280
Bye.

475
00:22:39,124 --> 00:22:41,525
What's wrong? Oh, I'm fine.

476
00:22:42,394 --> 00:22:44,625
Please, what's the
matter? Nope, it's nothing.

